# Artifact path disclosure

Whenever you **create or update** files in this workspace as part of the ASIC / pyCircuit workflow (architecture plans, verification docs, design notes, DUT source, generated summaries, etc.), end the response with a **Written artifacts** section (or equivalent) listing **repo-relative** paths—directory and filename for each file.

- If nothing was written (chat-only), state that explicitly (e.g. **`Written artifacts: none`**).
- Applies to the main agent and to behavior aligned with **`asic-arch-master-planner`**, **`asic-verification-mastermind`**, and **`pycircuit-implementation-engineer`**.
